sequenceDiagram
    participant Editor
    participant EditorEndpoint as Editor Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant Typology as AgentTypology (Domain)
    participant DB
    participant AdminEndpoint as Admin Endpoint
    participant Admin
    participant Events

    Note over Editor,Events: Phase 1: Editor Proposal

    Editor->>EditorEndpoint: POST /api/v1/agent-typologies/propose
    Note right of Editor: {name, description, basePrompt, strategy, phaseModels}

    EditorEndpoint->>Mediator: Send(ProposeAgentTypologyCommand)
    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>Typology: AgentTypology.Create(...)
    Typology->>Typology: Set Status = Draft
    Typology->>Typology: Set ProposedBy = EditorId
    Typology->>Events: Raise TypologyProposedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(typology)
    DB-->>Handler: Typology saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish TypologyProposedEvent
    Events-->>Admin: Notification: New typology proposed

    Handler-->>Editor: 201 Created {id, status: "Draft"}

    Note over Editor,Events: Phase 2: Editor Tests Typology

    Editor->>EditorEndpoint: POST /api/v1/agent-typologies/{id}/test
    Note right of Editor: {testQuery, gameId}

    EditorEndpoint->>Mediator: Send(TestAgentTypologyCommand)
    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>Handler: Invoke agent with test query
    Handler->>DB: Record test result
    DB-->>Handler: Result saved ✓

    Handler-->>Editor: {success: true, confidence: 0.85}

    Note over Editor,Events: Phase 3: Admin Reviews & Approves

    Admin->>AdminEndpoint: GET /api/v1/admin/agent-typologies/pending
    AdminEndpoint-->>Admin: List with test results

    Admin->>AdminEndpoint: POST /api/v1/admin/agent-typologies/{id}/approve
    Note right of Admin: {notes: "Approved"}

    AdminEndpoint->>Mediator: Send(ApproveAgentTypologyCommand)
    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Find typology
    DB-->>Handler: Typology found

    Handler->>Typology: Approve(adminId)
    Typology->>Typology: Set Status = Approved
    Typology->>Typology: Set ApprovedBy = AdminId
    Typology->>Events: Raise TypologyApprovedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(typology)
    DB-->>Handler: Updated ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish TypologyApprovedEvent
    Events-->>Editor: Notification: Your typology was approved!

    Handler-->>Admin: {id, status: "Approved"}
